This is a knowledge base of the network M-net which describes the nodes and the links of this network.
Every nodes of M-net are connected to other nodes with link.
 M-net is described with a graph that describes how the nodes are connected to each other. 
NetworkNode is the entity that describes the nodes of the network  M-net.
The nodes have the following property:
1) name is the name of  the node	
2) cost is the cost of the node	
3) posx is the x coordinate of the node
4) posy is the y coordinate of the node
5) sla is the service level agreement of the node
The links between nodes have the following property:
1) dist is the cost of the link between the nodes
